{
  "stem": "10478.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in order to give a good impression, they emptied the  prison for those people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So like me and others, we were allowed to go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about three months in that prison, yet, until October, 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before you were arrested the first time, were you ever trained in how to be interrogated?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did they ever give you any training on that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nobody.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only thing I had in that cell was a man who was from the Dutch intelligence service.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I had to appear before the court, the court martial, he had little pills, pep pills.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, [INAUDIBLE] he take one, he said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you'll be more alert, and you know what you're going to say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he said, also, don't answer them in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Act if you don't understand German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that way, you get a translator, and they give you time to think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But as a result of that pep pill, I was answering before the guy was finished with translating everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was OK, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had not enough evidence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] They thought we were trying to liberate a friend, out of the-- Derk Van Assen-- out of the prison.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had no success.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They shot Van Assen, but they didn't want to admit   it there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they acted, you know, he was still rescued, but not by them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The liberation occurred, for me, not in the southern part of Holland, what happened in September, 1944.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it happened to me in May 1945, when I was in Utrecht with-- with some family, [INAUDIBLE] for the second time  I was released from prison.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stayed with some family.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
